{% extends "email/base.twig" %}
{% block content %}
    <p>Hi {{ name }},</p>
    <p>Last week, we asked you to confirm your group’s membership by completing the payment and choosing a password. We think this might have slipped your mind. But don’t worry—it’s not too late!</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 30px">Pay and activate your membership in just a few clicks:</p>
    <a style="color: #102438;" class="button" href="{{ activationUrl }}">I choose a password</a>
    <a style="color: #102438;" class="button" href="{{ url }}">Password set! I complete my payment</a>
    <p style="margin-top: 40px">Activate your membership within 7 days to ensure access to your group account.</p>
    <p><u>Extra info on your membership:</u></p>
    <ul>
        <li>As a Hi Flanders member, your group will enjoy <a style="color: #fac000;" href="https://www.hiflanders.be/en/premium">exclusive benefits, discounts</a> and <a style="color: #fac000;" href="https://www.hiflanders.be/en/experiences">inspiration</a> for upcoming trips. But don’t worry, we won’t flood your inbox with emails. <strong>You stay in control</strong> and decide how often you hear from us.</li>
        <li>We handle your data confidentially and securely, in accordance with applicable privacy laws. Check our <a style="color: #fac000;" href="https://www.hiflanders.be/en/privacy-policy">privacy policy</a> for more details.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><u>Need help?</u></p>
    <p>Do you have any questions or trouble activating your membership? Feel free to contact us at <a style="color: #fac000;" href="mailto:hi@hiflanders.be">hi@hiflanders.be</a> or call <a style="color: #fac000;" href="tel:+3232327218">+32 3 232 72 18</a> during office hours.</p>
    <p>Looking forward to welcoming you and your group to one of our hostels soon!</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 30px">Warm regards,</p>
    <p><strong>The Hi Flanders Team</strong></p>
{% endblock %}